Spectator friends, the women's volleyball competition has begun.

现在是古巴女排发球。
Xi&#224;nz&#224;i sh&#236; G&#468;b&#257; n&#474;p&#225;i f&#257;qi&#250;.  
The Cuban women's volleyball team is serving now.

中国队接球不错。
