Team Cuba's defense is also very strong.

双人拦网。
Shu&#257;ngr&#233;n l&#225;nw&#462;ng.  
Two-person block at the net.

扣球！
N&#464; hu&#236; k&#257;ich&#275; ma?  
Spike!

啊呀，出界了。
